{
  "stem": "8842.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They knew that where we coming from, and they are very happy to announce to us that we finally can go home, which goes-- which is in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One of my girlfriends and myself-- at this point we learned how to ride horses, because you have to know how to ride a horse on a farm-- and we were moving those cows towards the place where they told us to go, which was another little city.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we met on the road a woman, and she asked us, are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I live-- I'm also on a farm like that, also deliberated by the Russians, and there's a man that came in and he came all the way from Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's looking for his family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he is-- he's looking for them, a wi-- his wife and his daughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's-- where is he?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she said, he's there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you want to go there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two of us ran to see him, and don't you believe this was my girlfriend's father, which was my sister's father-in-law.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now he came from Dachau when he was deliberated by the Germ-- by the American army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he immediately started to find out, looking for where women and children were left and where they were.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from place to place he was told where to go to keep looking for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With 300 kilometers walking and looking and searching, and he found us there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is-- this is-- this is-- nobody did anything like it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the two of us fell on him, and it was just unbelievable, an unbelievable, unbelievable feeling.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm crying and screaming, how wonderful to see him.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
